---
import { CLI_NAME } from '../constants';
---

<section class="features">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="feature-grid">
			<div class="feature-card">
				<h3><span class="feature-icon">★</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Discover</h3>
				<p>Discover the community extensions you can start using today.</p>
				<div class="code-example">
					<code>{CLI_NAME} list</code>
				</div>
				<div class="code-output">
					<span class="output-info">→</span>&nbsp;Available extensions:<br/>
					<span class="output-muted">NAME            VERSION  TYPE
coraza-waf      0.3.0    go
ip-restriction  1.2.0    rust</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="feature-card">
				<h3><span class="feature-icon">▶</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Run</h3>
				<p>Start Envoy with extensions in a single command.</p>
				<div class="code-example">
					<code>{CLI_NAME} run --extension example-go</code>
				</div>
				<div class="code-output">
					<span class="output-info">→</span>&nbsp;Fetching example-go...<br/>
					<span class="output-success">✓</span>&nbsp;Starting Envoy 1.37.0...<br/>
					<span class="output-muted">Proxy: http://localhost:10000<br/>Admin: http://localhost:9901</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="feature-card">
				<h3><span class="feature-icon">⤴</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Build</h3>
				<p>Easily bootstrap and create your own extension.</p>
				<div class="code-example">
					<code>{CLI_NAME} create my-extension</code>
				</div>
				<div class="code-output">
					<span class="output-info">→</span> Scaffolding "my-extension"...<br/>
					<span class="output-muted">./my-extension/Makefile</span>
					<span class="output-muted">./my-extension/manifest.yaml</span>
					<span class="output-muted">./my-extension/plugin.go</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
